Class PinkDoor

java.lang.Object
GameObject
Tile
LockedDoor
PinkDoor
public class PinkDoor extends LockedDoor
A class representing a locked pink door in the game. The door is initially locked and can be unlocked by a PinkKey. Once unlocked, the door is removed from the map.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Ollie Jones

      public void unlock(Map map, ArrayList<Key> keychain)
